data.description: Welcome to 523 Glenrose Lane, where comfort and charm meet in this delightful 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom house nestled in West Clermont school district. This lovely property offers a cozy and inviting atmosphere that will make you feel right at home. Step outside into your very own backyard oasis. Imagine hosting BBQs on your back yard patio while enjoying the warmth of the fire pit on cool evenings. The fenced-in back yard provides privacy and security. To top it all off, this house comes with a detached garage, providing additional storage space and keeping your vehicles safe from the elements. Don't miss out on this wonderful opportunity to call 523 Glenrose Lane your home. Schedule your showing today and start envisioning your new chapter in this fantastic property!
